			"body": "> Hello, what issue this is fixing?\r\n\r\nwhen use --profile \"data\\profile\" to run joplin, and write a note with \"$1$\", it will display \"11\" at right side, because the stylesheet will be link to \"resources/app.asar/gui/note-viewer/data/profile/\" but not \"data/profile/\", this pr will fix it.",
